Father in heaven,How we love You,We lift Your Name
 
In all the earth.

May Your kingdom be established

In our praisesAs Your people declareYour mighty works.

Blessed be the Lord God Almighty

Who was and is and is to come.

Blessed be the Lord God AlmightyWho reigns forevermore.

